latestIgtvVideos.caption:
They said I shouldn't or couldn't sing so I figured my way to sing. 
I might have loud and bold voice but that ain't gonna stop me from singing. Also this video is of me practising this amazing rap by @mostlysane at literally 7am becoz we weren't allowed to go on or even near that stage (#schoolrules 😂😂) But it was really so much fun. And i am posting it because why not. Also it was in one of  @mostlysane vlogs other than this rap when I saw or noticed @raftaarmusic for the 1st time And after that literally I have been such a big fan of @raftaarmusic (him) and all of his work. Thank u so much always inspiring @mostlysane &@raftaarmusic. And plz excuse the bad video quality.
Also thanks @goofy_charlie_ for capturing the moment and @gunjan.motwani for doing the aaye haaye haaye aye part😂
